Waterpik PowerPulse Hand-Held Showerhead in Chrome
data.description: Enjoy a powerful massage every day while taking a shower. The Waterpik Hand-Held Shower Head comes equipped with PowerPulse Massage, a massage technology that delivers up to 2X the massage force of other retail market showerheads.

data.title: Waterpik PowerSpray+Dual Showerhead in Chrome
data.description: Enhance your showering experience with the innovative Waterpik PowerSpray+Dual Showerhead. Boasting 5 different spray settings and a 3-way diverter lets you switch between the handheld, fixed mount showers, or for use of both at the same time.

data.title: Waterpik Rainfall Showerhead with Arm in Chrome
data.description: Bring traditional beauty to your bathroom with this elegant Rainfall Showerhead from Waterpik. Boasting a sleek, chrome finish, this showerhead features a large 6-inch face that creates a soothing overhead rainfall and an adjustable arm.
